139<lb/>
&amp; becomes common heat of temperature,<lb/>
&amp; consequently those bodies that reflect<lb/>
least heat, become hottest when exposed<lb/>
to radiant Heat, |_ &amp; with regard to<lb/>
colours, there is the inverse order.<lb/>
A thermometer painted white would be<lb/>
